{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About the game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pixel Quest: Guild is an idle RPG designed to stay at the bottom of the screen, hire and upgrade heroes in the town, when you are ready, take them to battle, the battle happens automatically and with each defeated monster they drop their soul, destroy the crystal and move on to the next stage, use these souls to further upgrade your buildings and heroes, and try to get past the boss!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224270/extras/GuildGif.gif?t=1729304224\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224270/extras/SteamGIf2_Heroes.gif?t=1729304224\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224270/extras/Guild_Leveling.gif?t=1729304224\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Mechanics</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prestige System: Earn medals by defeating certain bosses, use these medals to improve your heroes even further, or to buy artifacts that grant some unique bonuses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Develop your own guild, level up each building to unlock new resources</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Heroes gain experience in auto-battle, so let them fight while you do other things</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hundreds of combinations of passives and skills for hired heroes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Boss fights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build your party of heroes any way you want, try building a balanced party or just rogues that attack the crystal directly!</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224270/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729304224","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_it